      <odd id="aspace_82eca6a827f0501065b32d1ffd1909f6">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-B (YRG 5-B), Accounting records and records of the Yale comptroller.</p>  
      </odd>
